name: Release v2.5.0
body:
Nebula Importer compatible with Nebula Graph v2.5.0

Features:
1. Support date/time/datetime/timestamp datatypes: https://github.com/vesoft-inc/nebula-importer/pull/152
2. Add support for wildcard filename: https://github.com/vesoft-inc/nebula-importer/pull/153

Bugfixes:
1. Fix dead clock caused by incorrect `USE` statement: https://github.com/vesoft-inc/nebula-importer/pull/144
2. fix wait for `afterPeriod`: https://github.com/vesoft-inc/nebula-importer/pull/150

Changes:
1. Add test and import `testify.assert` tool: https://github.com/vesoft-inc/nebula-importer/pull/146

name: Release v2.0.0-ga
body: Nebula Importer compatible with Nebula Graph v2.0.0-ga

name: Release v1.0.0
body:
1. Add `preStop/postStart` support
2. Add `removeTempFiles` support to cleanup generated temporary files
3. Import data file shared by http(s) protocol
4. Upgrade nebula go version to v1.0.0
5. Add `retry` option
6. Specify csv column `index` of each field for tag or edge properties
7. Support multiple nebula graph server connections
